Package: SteadyStateBVAR
Title: Bayesian Vector Autoregression Models with Steady-State Priors via Stan
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Mark", "Becker", email = "mark.jw.becker@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Provides estimation of Bayesian Vector Autoregression ('BVAR') models
    with steady-state priors via 'Stan'. After estimation, the package provides functions for
    unconditional and conditional forecasting, and impulse response analysis. For more details
    on the steady-state BVAR model see Villani (2009) <doi:10.1002/jae.1065>.
